From: Andrew Morton <>
Subject: Re: [patch -mm] i386: use pte_update_defer in ptep_test_and_clear_{dirty,young}
Sender: linux-kernel-owner@vger.kernel.org
Precedence: bulk
List-ID: <linux-kernel.vger.kernel.org>
